; Minimal qfasm2 size extension from N224 through N232.
;
; Load after qfasm-n224-ext.qf1.  The nested normal-printer fixture has no
; labels past the N224 range, but its total segment size is N232, so the ELF
; header needs just this additional size path.

(Inc N224) N225
(Inc N225) N226
(Inc N226) N227
(Inc N227) N228
(Inc N228) N229
(Inc N229) N230
(Inc N230) N231
(Inc N231) N232

(FileSize N232) (Bytes 3C 01 00 00)
